item.title: [C4D] Psycola
item.dc:creator: @SomethingToHide STH
item.description:
@SomethingToHide wrote:

[quote=“ThAt0n36Uy, post:6, topic:213616”]Ok, the cone from the middle of the can to lip of the top half is too narrow.
The can on the left is too short. The lighting on cans make them look like a hexagon rather than a perfect cylinder. The tab on the can on the right is to large in comparison to the top. Nutrition labels do not usually stretch past the mid section of the can. The logo is stretched too much West to East on the left can.

The Left can’s shadow is only around the maximum width of the can, rather than the actual base, making it look like the can is glowing. I don’t know if that was on purpose, but I think it’d look better if the shadow was at the base.[/quote]

Both the cans are the exact same size btw, and they’re not modeled after a coke can. Logos aren’t stretched either, I actually shrunk them like 5%
